overlap.description:
Zones of different sensors overlap within the same room:

{overlaps}

Same-room separation relies on non-overlapping distance intervals — overlap means both sensors will claim the same target. This is a warning, not an error: submit to keep the configuration anyway, or adjust it later via Configure.

